vaazhthugal ( english : greetings ) is a 2008 indian tamil drama film written and directed by seeman .   the film features madhavan and bhavana in the lead roles along with venkat prabhu , ilavarasu , na .   muthusamy and r. k , who play supporting roles .   produced by siva for amma creations and with music scored by yuvan shankar raja , vaazhthugal was released on 14 january 2008 during pongal .